-- Adidas to Cut Product Range by Quarter to Reach Goals, FAZ Says
-- B y   C o r n e l i u s   R a h n
-- 2012-04-06T13:16:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-04-06/adidas-to-cut-product-range-by-quarter-to-reach-goals-faz-says.html
Adidas AG (ADS)  plans to reduce its
portfolio of about 47,000 products by a quarter to help it reach
earnings targets,  Frankfurter Allgemeine Zeitung  reported,
citing Chief Executive Officer Herbert Hainer.  The sporting-goods maker is also introducing a simplified
rebate system for its wholesale operations, helping it spend
less on discounts, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Cornelius Rahn in Frankfurt at 
 crahn2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kenneth Wong at 
 kwong11@bloomberg.net  